Name: GeographicStructureSchemeName
Description: A name for the GeographicStructure. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the GeographicStructure. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the GeographicStructure. May be expressed in multiple languages and supports the use of structured content.

Name: GeographicStructureSchemeReference
Description: The inclusion of an existing GeographicStructureScheme in the parent scheme by reference.

Name: GeographicStructureReference
Description: Used to describe any level of geography, including overall coverage and each of the lower levels.

Name: GeographicStructureGroupReference
Description: In-line description of a group of GeographicStructure.
